org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm

Class ACAQIteratingAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm.ACAQGraphNode
      • org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm.ACAQAlgorithm
        • org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm.ACAQIteratingAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ACAQValidatable, ACAQParallelizedAlgorithm, ACAQParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImageRoiProcessorAlgorithm, MacroWrapperAlgorithm, MergeChannelsAlgorithm, ReferencedAppendRectangularRoiAlgorithm, ReferencedDefineRectangularRoiAlgorithm, RemoveBorderRoisAlgorithm, RoiToMaskAlgorithm, RoiToRGBAlgorithm

    public abstract class ACAQIteratingAlgorithm
extends ACAQAlgorithm
implements ACAQParallelizedAlgorithm
    An ACAQAlgorithm that iterates through each data row. This algorithm utilizes the ACAQDataInterface class to iterate through input data sets. It offers various parameters that control how data sets are matched. If your algorithm only has one input and will never have more than one input slot, we recommend using ACAQSimpleIteratingAlgorithm instead that comes without the additional data set matching strategies
